@NODE Main "VWM, Virtual Window Manager, version 1.5"

  @{B}VWM, Virtual Window Manager, version 1.5@{UB}
  All concept, design and programming by Bahman Moallem.
  For AMIGA - AmigaOS 2.04 and better.


  VWM, the virtual screen aware window manager, is a small, fast,
  and system friendly virtual screen aware program that gives you
  100% control over windows' positions.


